261
00:14:26,652 --> 00:14:28,655
Thanks for listenin', kid.

262
00:14:30,824 --> 00:14:32,659
Hey, Santa,
what's shakin', man?

263
00:14:32,784 --> 00:14:36,497
What's your name, Bart... ner?
Uh, little partner?

264
00:14:36,623 --> 00:14:39,793
- I'm Bart Simpson. Who are you?
