265
00:14:39,793 --> 00:14:42,296
Oh, yeah?
We'll just see about that.

266
00:14:42,421 --> 00:14:45,007
D'oh!

267
00:14:45,090 --> 00:14:48,887
- Homer!
- A word with you in Santa's workshop.

268
00:14:49,012 --> 00:14:52,308
- Cover for me, Elfie.
- I didn't know it was you.

269
00:14:52,391 --> 00:14:54,393
Nobody knows.
It's a secret.

270
00:14:54,393 --> 00:14:56,395
I didn't get my bonus this year.

271
00:14:56,395 --> 00:14:58,690
But to keep the family
from missing out on Christmas,

272
00:14:58,690 --> 00:15:00,609
- I'd do anything.
- I'll say, Dad.

273
00:15:00,692 --> 00:15:03,904
you must really love us
