276
00:15:09,327 --> 00:15:11,330
Hey, little ones. Santa's back.

277
00:15:11,413 --> 00:15:13,415
Ho ho-- D'oh!

278
00:15:13,499 --> 00:15:16,294
Damn it to--

279
00:15:16,419 --> 00:15:18,630
Ah, son, one day
you're gonna know...

280
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,632
the satisfaction of payday.

281
00:15:20,632 --> 00:15:24,011
Receiving a big fat check
for a job well done.

282
00:15:24,095 --> 00:15:26,013
Simpson, Homer?
Here ya go.

283
00:15:26,097 --> 00:15:30,602
Come on, son. Let's go cash
this baby and get presents for--

284
00:15:30,602 --> 00:15:33,522
Thirteen bucks? Hey, wait a minute.

285
00:15:33,605 --> 00:15:35,525
That's right.
$120 gross.

286
00:15:35,608 --> 00:15:37,527
Less Social Security,
less unemployment insurance,

287
00:15:37,610 --> 00:15:39,612
- less Santa training...
- Santa training?

288
00:15:39,612 --> 00:15:41,615
less costume purchase,
less beard rental, less Christmas club.

289
00:15:41,699 --> 00:15:43,826
- But-- But--
- See ya next year.

290
00:15:43,951 --> 00:15:47,038
- Ohh!
- Come on, Dad. Let's go home.

291
00:15:47,038 --> 00:15:48,999
Thirteen bucks?

292
00:15:48,999 --> 00:15:51,334
you can't get anything
for 13 bucks.

293
00:15:51,459 --> 00:15:54,463
Allright!
Thirteen bigones!

294
00:15:54,505 --> 00:15:56,632
Springfield Downs,
here I come!

295
00:15:56,632 --> 00:15:58,968
- What?
- you heard me.

296
00:15:59,010 --> 00:16:00,971
I'm goin' to the dog track.

297
00:16:01,013 --> 00:16:03,015
I got a hot little puppy
in the fourth race.

298
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:05,142
- Wanna come?
- Sory, Barney.

299
00:16:05,142 --> 00:16:08,479
I may be a total washout as a father,
but I'm not gonna take my kid...

300
00:16:08,521 --> 00:16:10,815
to a sleazy dog track
on Christmas Eve.

301
00:16:10,982 --> 00:16:14,653
Come on, Simpson.
The dog's name is Whirlwind.

302
00:16:14,737 --> 00:16:17,156
Ten-to-one shot.
Money in the bank.

303
00:16:17,156 --> 00:16:19,159
- Uh-uh.
- Ah, come on, Dad.

304
00:16:19,159 --> 00:16:22,037
This can be the miracle that
saves the Simpsons' Christmas.

305
00:16:22,162 --> 00:16:24,040
If TV has taught me anything,

306
00:16:24,165 --> 00:16:27,168
