myself against such onslaughts.

356
00:18:57,927 --> 00:19:01,097
Mm-hmm. Go watch
your cartoon show, dear.

357
00:19:01,097 --> 00:19:03,100
Come on, Bart.

358
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,936
Kiss the ticket for good luck,
not that we need it.

359
00:19:09,274 --> 00:19:11,609
Here comes
Screwy the mechanical rabbit.

360
00:19:11,609 --> 00:19:13,236
