370
00:19:40,184 --> 00:19:43,646
- Come on, you stupid dog! Come on!
- Go, go!

371
00:19:43,688 --> 00:19:45,941
- Run! Run!
- Run, run! Come on, get that rabbit!

372
00:19:46,025 --> 00:19:48,736
