00:19:55,535 --> 00:19:58,956
Doesn't seem possible,
but I guess TV has betrayed me.

376
00:19:58,956 --> 00:20:01,542
I don't wanna leave
till our dog finishes.

377
00:20:06,757 --> 00:20:08,634
Ah, forget it.
Let's go.

378
00:20:17,853 --> 00:20:20,564
- Find any winners, son?
- Sory, Dad.

379
00:20:20,648 --> 00:20:23,652
Hey, hey, Simpson!
What'dl tell you?

380
00:20:23,652 --> 00:20:26,947
Whirlwind!
Let's go, Daria.

381
